## 5. Data Models

### MainFolder
```json
{
  "id": "string",
  "name": "string",
  "subdomains": [ "Subdomain" ],
  "department": "string"
}
```

### Subdomain
```json
{
  "id": "string",
  "name": "string",
  "files": [ "FileItem" ]
}
```

### FileItem
```json
{
  "id": "string",
  "name": "string",
  "revisions": [ "FileRevision" ],
  "category": "string",
  "department": "string"
}
```

### FileRevision
```json
{
  "id": "string",
  "fileName": "string",
  "revision": "string",
  "uploadedBy": "string",
  "uploadedDate": "ISO String",
  "approvalStatus": "pending" | "approved" | "rejected",
  "isLatest": true
}
```
